  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_b6955d20-b38a-4ed7-addc-0d5e048becbd" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Security</strong> tab.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>The Security tab only displays in Account Settings if you have <a href="/t5/Admin-Guide/How-do-I-manage-feature-options-for-an-account/ta-p/204" target="_blank">enabled the Content Security Policy feature</a> option.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
